都算！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"不想說明，只想反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207e890cae8ab5d33a7adb0c0fbd71a8edd70fb3","tid":2245745,"uid":221004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ef22bc2a95e52850d9a82b4ba7809113964c5b","tid":2245745,"uid":231583,"like":136,"dislike":2,"score":134,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbfcf098469375444ad3caa21f20e115acc11ac","tid":2245745,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c5e6ff5603370641daab230b88da949a8af7ae5","tid":2245745,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">蓬佩奧揚言關閉美境所有孔子學院 中國 : 必遭「有識之士」堅決抵制</span></strong><br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 蕭達多 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2020.10.16 | 17:29<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/481/5f88e69464644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F481%2F5f88e69464644.jpg&h=253add7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國孔子學院打著文化交流的旗幟，進行為中國共產黨宣傳之實，據點遍布全球，如今已經引起警戒。   圖：翻攝自孔子學院官網<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）今日表示，美國孔子學院年底前全部關閉。對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅今 (16) 日回應，蓬佩奧等政治人物污衊孔子學院，蓄意破壞中美人文教育交流，嚴重違背兩國民意。</span><br />\n<br />\n據外電報導，蓬佩奧與美教育部長德沃斯共同發信給各級學校，內容引述國務院教育和文化事務局的審查，表示孔子學院實際為中國政府的重要宣傳工具，以文化交流與教導中文作為偽裝，實際上致力在教育界發揮影響力。而且，孔子課堂上的老師會被定期進行審查，以避免批評中國政府的言行。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅表示，孔子學院是幫助各國人民學習中文、了解中國、加強中國與各國人文交流。中美大學相互尊重、友好協商、平等互利的原則合作成立的。其運作管理公開透明、嚴格遵守當地法律及大學各項規範，促進中美人文交流作出了積極貢獻，受到所在大學和美國人民的廣泛歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅稱，蓬佩奧等美國一些政客出於意識形態偏見和一己政治私利，污衊抹黑孔子學院，干擾其在美國的正常運作，蓄意破壞中美人文和教育交流合作，嚴重違背兩國民意，必將遭到美國「有識之士」的堅決抵制。<br />\n<br />\n最後趙立堅呼籲美方，停止將有關教育交流項目政治化，停止干擾中美之間正常的人文交流，停止損害中美之間的互信與合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-16/480350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-10-16%2F480350&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU4OqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=c9a745c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-16/480350</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"點解全部都力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0496daf4d62a97e2b0ab8468f1d87082b891de6","tid":2245745,"uid":308440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"敢做就保留反應?? 即係劣呀?"},{"pid":"193695272eaf931fbe0ab2437f4112891a3b6428","tid":2245745,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">唔比國民去美國</span>"},{"pid":"b485a027f32fb9892593edecf56b2808086d5d31","tid":2245745,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"打啦 好悶呀"},{"pid":"86cfb6979744158ce52cc4087273bba47d1109c6","tid":2245745,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"黎黎去去都係呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ceda4c20f017f4dd46c32c6160135fdccaa4e8e","tid":2245745,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hk